---
title: Beef Fried Rice with Green Beans and Red Pepper
description: Quick, delicious and easy to prep, our beef fried rice with green beans and red peppers is a winning recipe for easy nights in. Beef mince, fresh veggies, soy sauce and steamed basmati rice, are tossed together with fresh lime juice and chopped coriander for a flavour combination you just can’t beat.
